import axios from 'axios' import React from 'react' import { useDispatch, useSelector } from 'react-redux' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' import { userLogOut } from '../../store/user' import SideBar from '../SideBar/SideBar' const NavBar = () => { const dispatch = useDispatch() const user = useSelector((state) => state.user) const handlerLogOut = () => { axios .post('/api/user/logOut') .then((res) => res.data) .then(() => dispatch(userLogOut())) .catch(() => alert('No se pudo cerrar sesion.')) } return (
TMDB {user.id ? ( <> ) : ( <> )}
) } export default NavBar
